title: Focus - Focus Con Proby (1977)
description:
Focus con Proby is the sixth studio album by the progressive rock band Focus. Featuring the American singer P. J. Proby, it was released in January 1978. The record also features guitarists Eef Albers and Philip Catherine, drummer Steve Smith, as well as the two Focus members from previous albums.
